Microsoft Entra External ID is Microsoft’s comprehensive solution for managing identities beyond internal employees.

It supports:

* Workforce external collaboration
* Customer identity
* Secure partner ecosystems

For example, organizations can build secure portals for customers and vendors.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is B2C customer login systems.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is multinational partner ecosystems.

Microsoft Entra External ID extends identity governance beyond organizational boundaries.
